  "summaries": [
    {
      "id": 20887,
      "category": "team",
      "content": "@Cryptographer reported if a logout request for a given session was received during the time a product creation request was in progress from the same session, it was possible the logout request could fail. We determined this was the result of a race condition in how we were updating and revoking user sessions and have since fixed the issue.",
